      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The bride&amp;#39;s mother must belong to a Scheduled Caste community.\n   1. Financial help is available for the marriage of up to two daughters in a family.\n   1. The bride must be at least 18 years old on the date of marriage.\n   1. This assistance is only for the first marriage of each daughter.\n   1. Your family&amp;#39;s monthly income cannot be more than ₹2,000/-. (Verified by the Tehsildar).\n   1. Applicant must have lived in Chandigarh for at least 3 years.\n   1. If both the bride&amp;#39;s parents are deceased, her legal guardian can apply for this help.\n\n",
